The objective is to build a responsive API with some SPA to show the design and the project goals building graduativaly, valuing simplicity of the Clean Code/Architecture. Technologies: .NET Core 5, Angular 12, Entity Framework Core as ORM.
PRÉ-REQUISITOS
1 - Instalar o NodeJS. NodeJS já vem com o npm Node Package Manager
2 - Instalar o .NET 5.0.102
3 - Instalar o Angular 12: npm install -g @angular/cli@12

ETAPAS
1 - Criar um projeto WebAPI: dotnet new webapi -n ProEventos.API (Utilize dotnet new webapi -h para mais informações)